overview:
Bizchum.com is a unique online marketplace where entrepreneurs can showcase their products for the world to see. It is an interactive marketplace that directly connects the sellers with the buyers and vice versa.

Bizchum.com is everybody’s business city where people can establish business connections from their own bedrooms to places around the word, where seller and buyer can build a business relationship, and perhaps even build friendships in the course of their business relationship!

Vision bizchum.com is under EVISORYA PHILIPPINES COMPANY, a Philippine company founded in 2007 by mother and son, Brenda and Bong, whose vision is that people with a passion for business can easily make business connections, even friendships, in just a click.
